Uses of Package
com.paydiant.android.core.domain

  • Packages that use com.paydiant.android.core.domain 
    Package Description
    com.paydiant.android.common.util
    Provides set of utility classes.
    com.paydiant.android.core.domain
    Domain objects that is used to transfer data between the SDK and the mobile gateway.
    com.paydiant.android.core.domain.account
    This package contains domain objects that can be used to perform operations on Payment Accounts using the meta-data driven approach.
    com.paydiant.android.core.domain.registerCustomer
    Domain objects that is used with federated identity user creation.
    com.paydiant.android.core.domain.splittender
    This package contains domain objects that can be used to perform operations on split tender transactions.
    com.paydiant.android.core.facade
    Contains the core facade service implementations.
    com.paydiant.android.core.service
    Contains the services to facilitate core facade services.
    com.paydiant.android.core.util.threads  
    com.paydiant.android.ui.service.account
    UI services and listener implementations for the account management related operations.
    com.paydiant.android.ui.service.captureToken.camera  
    com.paydiant.android.ui.service.customer
    UI services and listener implementations for the customer management related operations.
    com.paydiant.android.ui.service.deviceinfo
    UI services and listener implementations to manage additional device info .
    com.paydiant.android.ui.service.offer
    UI services and listener implementations for managing offers.
    com.paydiant.android.ui.service.receipt
    UI services and listener implementations for viewing information about the receipts.
    com.paydiant.android.ui.service.security
    UI services and listener implementations for the user management related operations.
    com.paydiant.android.ui.service.transaction
    UI services and listener implementations for management of transactions.
    com.paydiant.android.ui.service.userregistration
    UI services and listener implementations for the user management related operations.
